&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;photo_img img&quot; src=&quot;http://sphotos-c.ak.fbcdn.net/hphotos-ak-prn1/s720x720/18729_10151316978802264_2032366785_n.jpg&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 620px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;caption&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Không gian tác phẩm cộng tác của lâm Hiếu Thuận và Lin Wan Yu | The installation view of the work by Lam hieu Thuan and Lin wan Yu&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
